≡ 
<taxonomicName id="A32139E80E7150CE455986B29C12EB02" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Marasmiaceae" genus="Crinipellis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Crinipellis brasiliensis" order="Agaricales" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">Crinipellis brasiliensis</taxonomicName>
Arruda, G.F.
<normalizedToken id="E2956DC24FA4AD3A16D39C44B4C364BC" originalValue="Sepúlveda">Sepulveda</normalizedToken>
, R.N.G.Miller, M.A.Ferreira &amp; M.S.Felipe, Mycologia 97: 1355 (2006). Type: Brazil. Minas Gerais, Itumirim. On dry fan brooms of 
<taxonomicName id="AE8D1E40DD2E3860ED35E78A68AA59CD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Marasmiaceae" genus="Heteropterys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Heteropterys acutifolia" order="Agaricales" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="acutifolia">Heteropterys acutifolia</taxonomicName>
